{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L775","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":true}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier